<use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104fcq1665703251101.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fcq1665703251101.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fcq1665703251101.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"fcq1665703251101\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify the library name for global objects needed by the application when the application starts. Libraries are typed, so each global object library can have the same name which functions as a shared namespace which can be specified by this setting.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"fcq1665703251101__topic_d143726e1_d143727e1_d143728e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fcq1665703251101__p_d143729e1_d143730e1_d143731e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$VARIATION</span> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>} <var class=\"keyword varname\">LibraryName</var></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fcq1665703251101__section_dk1_wwm_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d712412e64\">Defaults</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"fcq1665703251101__table_d17042e1_d17043e1_d17044e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Assignment file:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Any application assignment file</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Section:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">[SETTINGS]</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">None</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fcq1665703251101__section_qkx_xwm_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d712412e110\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fcq1665703251101__p_d143738e1_d143739e1_d143740e1\">The value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$VARIATION</span>\n            determines the library used to locate the following resources at runtime:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"fcq1665703251101__ul_rzj_zwm_lwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fcq1665703251101__li_d50252e1_d50253e1_d50254e1\">Messages </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fcq1665703251101__li_d50255e1_d50256e1_d50257e1\">Help texts </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fcq1665703251101__li_d50258e1_d50259e1_d50260e1\">Menus </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fcq1665703251101__li_d50261e1_d50262e1_d50263e1\">Panels </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fcq1665703251101__li_d50264e1_d50265e1_d50266e1\">Glyphs </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fcq1665703251101__li_d50267e1_d50268e1_d50269e1\">Device translation tables </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fcq1665703251101__li_d50270e1_d50271e1_d50272e1\">Keyboard translation tables </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fcq1665703251101__li_d50273e1_d50274e1_d50275e1\">Language setups </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fcq1665703251101__p_d143741e1_d143742e1_d143743e1\">For example, by setting\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$VARIATION</span> to <code class=\"ph codeph\">MYAPP</code>, you instruct Uniface to look\n            for global objects in the libraries of this name. By setting\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$LANGUAGE</span>, you can specify which language-specific libraries to\n            use for messages, menus, and glyphs. For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"fcq1665703251101__pre_xwj_zwm_lwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[SETTINGS]\n$VARIATION = MyApp\n$LANGUAGE = FRA</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fcq1665703251101__p_d143744e1_d143745e1_d143746e1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$VARIATION</span> also determines the\n            keyboard or device translation table loaded if <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$KEYBOARD</span> or\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$DISPLAY</span> are specified.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fcq1665703251101__p_d143747e1_d143748e1_d143749e1\">The value defined by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$VARIATION</span>\n            can be tested or overridden at runtime using the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$variation</span>\n            ProcScript function.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zum1665703230237.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$LANGUAGE</a><p>Specify the language to use for global objects and language setups.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/icm1665703229996.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$KEYBOARD</a><p>Specify a translation table for input characters.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zkc1665703224453.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$DISPLAY</a><p>Specify a translation table for display in character-based user interface (CHUI).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/exe1665702665391.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$variation</a><p>Return or specify the name of the library containing objects needed by the application or component.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/loi1665702847852.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Global Objects</a><p>A global object is a reusable, technology-independent object that is centrally stored and available to all components running on a given host, regardless of the deployment environment.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527446\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527446\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$VARIATION Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Specify the library name for global objects needed by the application when the application starts. Libraries are typed, so each global object library can have the same name which functions as a shared namespace which can be specified by this setting. $VARIATION { = } LibraryName Defaults Assignment file: Any application assignment file Section: [SETTINGS] Default value: None Description The value of $VARIATION determines the library used to locate the following resources at runtime: Messages Help texts Menus Panels Glyphs Device translation tables Keyboard translation tables Language setups For example, by setting $VARIATION to MYAPP , you instruct Uniface to look for global objects in the libraries of this name. By setting $LANGUAGE , you can specify which language-specific libraries to use for messages, menus, and glyphs. For example: [SETTINGS] $VARIATION = MyApp $LANGUAGE = FRA Copy $VARIATION also determines the keyboard or device translation table loaded if $KEYBOARD or $DISPLAY are specified. The value defined by $VARIATION can be tested or overridden at runtime using the $variation ProcScript function. Related Links $LANGUAGE Specify the language to use for global objects and language setups. $KEYBOARD Specify a translation table for input characters. $DISPLAY Specify a translation table for display in character-based user interface (CHUI). $variation Return or specify the name of the library containing objects needed by the application or component. Global Objects A global object is a reusable, technology-independent object that is centrally stored and available to all components running on a given host, regardless of the deployment environment. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}